<plot>Two struggling actors decide to take a road trip to burn off the stress of the big city and to try and overcome a career ending writers block. The career writing partners find that the road and stress become too much. Bad idea after bad idea leads to frustration and animosity. David Ballam and Justin Taite take the open road in their 1991 Jetta to find the truth behind their writing skills and their relationship.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?464891</url></doc>
